- **[P2] No empty state** â€” Empty items shows nothing. Fixed: added empty state message.
- **[P2] No user-facing error feedback** â€” Errors only in console. Fixed: added error state and UI display.

- **[P1] Hardcoded error strings** (lines 20,33) â€” "Fetch failed"/"Delete failed" not using i18n. Fixed: replaced with `t('test_page.fetch_failed')` / `t('test_page.delete_failed')`.
- **[P2] No loading/disabled state on Delete button** (lines 50-55) â€” Double-click causes duplicate DELETEs. Fixed: added `deletingId` state, disabled button during delete.
- **[P2] Error state never cleared on success** (lines 24,36) â€” Stale error persists after successful actions. Fixed: added `setError(null)` at start of fetchItems and deleteItem.
- **[P2] List items lack flex layout** (line 48) â€” Name and button stack vertically on mobile. Fixed: added `flex items-center justify-between` to item div.
